      <button>
        What time does the anomaly start?
      </button>
   
      <p>We don't know the answer yet, but historically an anomaly does not officially start until afternoon.
        We will give you more specific timings once Niantic releases them. However, your team may decide to
        meet up earlier in the day so that everyone can get to know each other.
      </p>



      <button>
        Can I still support my team if I cannot attend?
      </button>
   

      <p>Yes, you can provide them items, set up farming events prior to the anomaly, and tell other people
        about the anomaly and where to sign up (here).
      </p>
